                &#39;body&#39; =&gt; $_POST[&#39;message&#39;]
            )
        );
    }
    
This way you do the sending in each iteration and avoiding create the array you overwrite.

  [1]: https://www.twilio.com/docs/sms/tutorials/how-to-send-sms-messages-php#sending-multiple-messages-or-a-message-to-multiple-recipients

